Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.23,0:01:35.57,Note,,0,0,0,,Kokogi Designer Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer vacation starts tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.39,0:01:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.03,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an2\b1\c&H171717&\bord0\shad0\fnSegoe Print\pos(716.666,192.5)}Summer Vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...my script for the summer Comic Stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an audition for a TV anime that starts in the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.09,0:01:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it'll be late night by the time we finish, so I don't think I can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask me again sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make time for you, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next time then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.58,0:02:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.87,0:02:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanako, what part are you reading for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuran, the magical ninja girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem pretty confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.31,0:02:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got the script down to a "T."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, tomorrow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Stab.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stab.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, villains!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.56,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an2\b1\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\fnSegoe Print\move(906.068,308.571,816.18,308.571,9,3491)\fs90.756\frx2\fry26\frz332.494}Summer Vacation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.99,0:03:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...so anyway, we're gonna talk about Jung today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Jung had a disagreement with Freud, apparently, and went in another direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:22.18,Background2,,0,0,0,,Jung apparently had a very hard time establishing his ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're alone in the park at night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:26.32,Background2,,0,0,0,,Then at last he published his theories of psychological types.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.03,0:03:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...in spite of what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she fine with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:33.23,Background2,,0,0,0,,On the basis of these cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,my conclusion is that you are an "Introverted Feeling" type.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.64,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You are frightened of the "Great Mother."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You are also fighting against your "Shadow."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't we cover that topic before?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Did... did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stop here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart doesn't seem to be in it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.87,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it together, Tatsuhiro Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.68,0:04:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,My instincts are telling me that to get too close to her is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know anything about her:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who she really is, or what her real purpose is either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She may be a secret operative of the Nihon Hikikomori Kyoukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sato, let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I really do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato! Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming in, Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.51,0:05:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hiding away in here as always, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been drinking, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I not supposed to? I'm over 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.24,0:05:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,By law, I'm allowed to consume alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.04,0:05:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's to the law: Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Drunks are a pain in the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, the rest of the world is on summer vacation already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time to be casually shutting yourself in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the beach! To the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! Her face is in my mind for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact is I don't have swim trunks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I can't do the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Sato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need swim trunks or anything to go to the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.69,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,For healthy young folk like us, summer at the beach can only mean one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Summer Comic Stall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer Comic Stall?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:38.21,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H1F1F1F&\bord1.513\3c&HA1A1A1&\frx30\fry30\pos(1145.169,485.546)\frz356.561}Comic Stall Venue
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.44,0:06:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, it's the ocean; I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd heard about a huge doujin sales exhibition during the summer and winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.94,0:06:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they hold it in this kind of place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people in my class got a booth at the Comic Stall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.35,0:06:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But we got to talking about how lame it would be if we only have one game to put out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.90,0:07:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,With only a third-rate game like that, there's no way any customers or anybody will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A game is a holistic work of art.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.40,0:07:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,To try to fake it by filling up holes in the game script with minigames along the way is too damn cynical!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell invited Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:17.94,Background2,,0,0,0,,Do you think like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the last drinking party of first term.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:20.64,Background2,,0,0,0,,You're all really too optimistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to at least try to invite everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.64,0:07:22.13,Background2,,0,0,0,,Your thinking is way too optimistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured, even if I invited him, he wouldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.67,Background2,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me, all of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:29.13,Background2,,0,0,0,,It's all really about how good a script you create!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.99,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he hasn't ever come to anything before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If the most crucial thing, the story, is lame, the players won't bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get even this most basic concept?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, can you make a more interesting one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I say I'm in the middle of making one with an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In high school he was head of the Literature Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so the script is flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're interested,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,shall I do you the honor of setting it out at your booth?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:08:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll teach you what a real game is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,My classmates were in tears, begging for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So I decided to put our game in their booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got less than a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a deadline, you'd just laze around and procrastinate, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, Sato, you know you're the one who started this talk of creating a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be a game creator, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Once my buzz wears off, we'll get to work immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We've only been given one month after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.31,0:08:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that laptop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's watch each other as we work to keep us from procrastinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:58.76,Background2,,0,0,0,,We will hold our annual fireworks display at the festival grounds in Kasenjiki Park tonight, starting at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:04.97,Background2,,0,0,0,,Please invite everybody and come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot, isn't it, Yamazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.47,0:09:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your A/C doesn't seem to be working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been temperamental since a little while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it finally gave out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:45.21,Background2,,0,0,0,,We will hold our annual fireworks display at the festival grounds in Kasenjiki park tonight, starting at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:51.24,Background2,,0,0,0,,Please invite everybody and come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki, want to go to the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have that kind of spare time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't a little mood change increase our work efficiency?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, it doesn't have to be fireworks, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No good comes out of going to see stupid fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No good at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamazaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.97,0:10:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished the color design for the heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped it into "Shared Files," so give it a check, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it looks pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The heroine Rei's secret is revealed in a classroom of the hero's school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing. I have nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.67,0:11:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.90,0:11:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You have me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you, even if it turns the whole world against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's, uh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does everything turn into her face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great, Yamazaki. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Before they journey off into a different world, the hero and Rei go to the beach to make memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, you come out here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind being seen if it's by you, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.62,0:12:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of this. How am I supposed to concentrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.54,0:13:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, why did she appear again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is her first outfit when they go to a different world, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That means this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.31,0:13:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.80,0:13:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell has come over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, you're worried about real-life romance, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki, was that her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:14:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've thought of nothing but her for a while now, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that I'm thinking of her;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,she just pops up in my head of her own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That must mean you're actually in love with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm in love with a girl like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ridiculous, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.32,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are just human beings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,All this "love" stuff doesn't exist in the three-dimensional world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.49,0:14:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Originally, romantic love didn't exist in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Arranged marriages and late-night trysts were all there were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This "romantic love" stuff is a custom that came in from overseas!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Romantic love is a trap to expand the capitalist system!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're gonna let it dance you around like a puppet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.24,0:14:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get on the other side of it and turn this "love" illusion into a way to make money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.76,0:14:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that, but what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you in love with that Nanako girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako's even the model for this heroine, isn't she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:26.44,Background2,,0,0,0,,We will hold our annual fireworks display at the festival grounds in Kasenjiki park tonight, starting at 7:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:32.77,Background2,,0,0,0,,Please invite everybody and come on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks displays can just vanish from this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on the brink of stupidly repeating the same mistake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The same mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.41,0:15:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It was when I was still in elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You dork!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nyah-nyah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:15:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb-head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You make me sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.14,0:16:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lame-o.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, Paruko's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody run for cover before she tells on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here! It's Paruko! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling Paruko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.80,0:16:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.89,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, that was my first crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was already set to transfer schools when the first term ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked her to the fireworks so I'd at least have a last remembrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.85,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But tomorrow I sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...sort of have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...go see my sick grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.14,0:17:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how my first crush ended all too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.17,0:17:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that had really been the end, I might still have been saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.12,0:17:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, villains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.08,0:17:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, villains!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Women lie with a straight face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Even that Nanako, all the while she was saying she had some audition,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm positive she's on a date with another guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The same goes for that Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.87,0:18:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for damn sure she's laughing at you, Sato the hikikomori, behind your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Women are a disease of this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.86,0:18:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to bring down the iron hammer of Justice upon the world's women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Sato, say it with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Get lost, women.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Too soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.68,0:18:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Put this on and try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, women.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Put more enmity into it and say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, women! Get lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.85,0:18:55.87,Background2,,0,0,0,,Get lost, women! Get lost, women! Get lost, women! Get lost, women!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.83,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonder who that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.86,Note,,0,0,0,,{\an2\blur4.537\c&HE4FFFF&\3c&H0F61A4&\shad0\fscx230\fscy147.5\frz335.067\pos(684.944,279.833)\frx16\fry2}Nanako-tan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.87,0:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you keep quiet for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.87,0:19:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? What's up with the sudden call?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, the audition suddenly got postponed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I remembered the fireworks display you were talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually at the station already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.38,0:19:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It's no problem for me at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come to meet you there. Wait there, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A change of mood is necessary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That being so, I'm going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sato, keep working hard on that script, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You can all get shot by fireworks and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.86,0:20:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have quite a while until counseling time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Misaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, it's about today's counseling... I'd like to cancel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,On that note...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.42,0:20:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you come with me to see the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Might this not be a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,After this, I'll bet there's going to be a big backlash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.16,0:21:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it's this kind of trap,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF9A08D&\pos(640,136.135)\fs60.504}Episode 9
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&HF4813F&\pos(640,468.907)\fs60.504}Welcome to a Summer Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.07,0:23:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You slipped up, Sato.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.84,0:23:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The heroine's name is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.88,0:23:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She was watching me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next episode, "Welcome to the Dark Side!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H8F908E&\pos(640,113.445)\fs60.504\fad(1148,0)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:40.00,Note,,0,0,0,,{\c&H525250&\pos(640,446.219)\fs60.504\fad(1148,0)}Welcome to the Dark Side!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:16.18,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,I lift my eyes a little and look into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.26,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,All I do is mutter every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.33,0:00:22.31,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,as I turn my back
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:24.64,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,on this perfect everyday life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:27.81,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,"Where am I supposed to go?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:32.86,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,With you who are giving me a look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.28,0:00:42.20,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,In the shadows of a back alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:49.33,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the hands of a clock repaint the time that has been stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:53.07,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Extended hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:57.44,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,puzzle pieces that don't fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:01.74,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Until the abandoned two
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.74,0:01:05.79,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,reunite with something
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:10.42,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,that has been lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:13.96,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,Recover
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.17,0:01:18.22,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,the last piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.09,0:01:24.35,OP_rus,,0,0,0,,and let's start walking.
